div.p:
—Describe a comprehensive framework within which the members of the
                            Alliance will pursue their economic, political, and security objectives;
                            and indicate the basic principles in each element of the
                            relationship—political, military, economic;

—Lay the basis for a new consensus on Alliance security requirements, as
                            well as for a rational and intelligible strategy, and equitable and
                            effective defense contributions to realize these objectives;
